{"tid":548188,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【Bitcoin狂潮】Bitcoin跌穿9000美元！日金融廳現場調查CoinCheck","createTime":"2018-02-02T09:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T09:21:00.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9befb3b25be123f7cce8d33ef68d6791131c7fcc","tid":548188,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T09:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180202/large/1517542289_6907.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180202%2Flarge%2F1517542289_6907.jpg&h=19129039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球政府對比特幣（Bitcoin）的監管愈來愈嚴密，致市場產生憂慮，Bitcoin曾低見8,690美元，去年12月曾升至20,000美元歷史高位，至今累跌50%以上。<br />\n<br />\n加密貨幣交易所Coincheck上月因被黑客盜取5.23億個NEM加密貨幣，日本財相麻生太郎表示，金融廳正對Coincheck進行現場檢查。此外，Facebook早前宣佈在社交平戓上禁止與Bitcoin和加密貨幣相關的廣告。<br />\n據CoinMarketCap資料顯示，Bitcoin最新跌12.88%，報8,867美元。2月份Bitcoin期貨CME報8,845美元，跌245美元，成交303張；Cboe報8,770美元，跌310美元，成交1,161張。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180202/57783619\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180202%2F57783619&d=Uy%2BW7RV8F6sDBdbTeXJrK2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=4ea03bbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180202%2F57783619&h=31340619\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180202/57783619</a>"},{"pid":"97c47fc1844329a2bca80779a20b907d8d441332","tid":548188,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T09:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ef80414a2b1d89cb5601e4f4b21c9c9944a358","tid":548188,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"97c47fc1844329a2bca80779a20b907d8d441332","tid":548188,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci